profile.description: LinkDelete is the first inbound link deletion investigation and one-way link reduction vendor meant to assist internet entrepreneurs cleanup their artificial one-way links and thus correct their Google search rankings. Immediately after back links have been completely defined we can then carry out backlinking removals as well as cleanups to get those non-organic back-links removed from the web.
